Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:47.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本気で　one more chance please
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:51.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いまより素敵な未来があるのに
